Package: bayesadapt
Title: Bayesian Adaptive Clinical-Trial Simulator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sseguya", "Solomon", , "sseguya256@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R Shiny (golem) simulator of Bayesian adaptive clinical trials,
    organised around the ADEMP framework. The MVP is a two-arm, binary-outcome
    design with a conjugate Beta-Binomial backend (no MCMC), posterior-probability
    stopping, and calibration of the superiority threshold to a target type I
    error under the null. Operating characteristics are reported with Monte-Carlo
    standard errors.
